OL,3,CDad of IPP Prisoner: 'how long do they
OL,4,Cwant to keep him... until he's in a
OL,5,Cbox?'
OL,7,FWatch Kris Jepson's report about Danny
OL,8,FWeatherson, who is still in prison 19
OL,9,Fyears after he attempted to steal a
OL,10,Fcoat and mobile phone
OL,12,FThe father of a Newcastle man, who has
OL,13,Fbeen in prison for 19 years because he
OL,14,Fattempted to steal a coat and mobile
OL,15,Fphone, has told ITV News it was a "set
OL,16,Fback" when the Labour Party failed to
OL,17,Fback a change to the parole process
OL,18,Fthis week in the House of Lords.
