OL,3,CDad of IPP Prisoner: 'how long do they
OL,4,Cwant to keep him... until he's in a
OL,5,Cbox?'
OL,7,FFor the low level crime Danny
OL,8,FWeatherson, 35, committed, he was told
OL,9,Fhe should have served just 15 months,
OL,10,Fbut he has now spent more than half
OL,11,Fhis life behind bars.
OL,13,FDanny Weatherson was released in
OL,14,FSeptember 2023 after serving 18 years
OL,15,Fin prison under an Imprisonment for
OL,16,FPublic Protection (IPP) sentence. IPPs
OL,17,Fwere abolished in 2012, but the cases
OL,18,Fwere not backdated, leaving nearly
OL,19,F3,000 prisoners still languishing in
OL,20,Fcells.
