OL,3,CDad of IPP Prisoner: 'how long do they
OL,4,Cwant to keep him... until he's in a
OL,5,Cbox?'
OL,7,FMaurice Stevens, Danny's dad, told ITV
OL,8,FNews: "Thousands of people around the
OL,9,Fcountry have been set back, yet again,
OL,10,Fbecause they could have been released,
OL,11,Flike within the next six months, 12
OL,12,Fmonths, instead of lying there for
OL,13,Fanother five years. They say on the
OL,14,Fone hand that they were given to the
OL,15,Fwrong type of offenders. Low level
OL,16,Foffenders doing a life sentence. It's
OL,17,Fjust so wrong. Somebody in prison for
OL,18,F19 years for a low level offence."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
