OL,3,CDad of IPP Prisoner: 'how long do they
OL,4,Cwant to keep him... until he's in a
OL,5,Cbox?'
OL,7,FHe went onto to explain that Danny has
OL,8,Frecently been diagnosed with
OL,9,FParkinson's disease, which has
OL,10,Fcompounded his anger at his son's
OL,11,Fongoing incarceration.
OL,13,FHe added: "I'm devastated, because
OL,14,Fwe've waited all this time. They've
OL,15,Falready took your kid away from you
OL,16,Ffor 19 years, and now they're telling
OL,17,Fyou that he's got a condition like
OL,18,FParkinson's disease... What do they
OL,19,Fwant from him? How long do they want
OL,20,Fto keep him for? Until he's in a box?"
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
